OL,3,CTheatre to re-open after help from
OL,4,Cfamous friends
OL,6,FA troubled theatre is to re-open after
OL,7,Fbeing closed for more than a year
OL,8,Ffollowing an intense campaign fronted
OL,9,Fby former Coronation Street actor
OL,10,FJulie Hesmondhalgh.
OL,12,FHundreds of protesters including other
OL,13,FNorth West acting stars voiced their
OL,14,Fsupport to save Oldham's Coliseum
OL,15,FTheatre after Arts Council England cut
OL,16,Fits grant to the venue, labelling it
OL,17,F"high risk".
OL,19,FThe theatre, on Fairbottom Street,
OL,20,Fclosed its doors in March 2023 just
OL,21,Fmonths after the announcement.
