OL,3,CTheatre to re-open after help from
OL,4,Cfamous friends
OL,6,FLater that year, Oldham Council's
OL,7,Fleader said the Coliseum theatre
OL,8,Fbuilding could not have been saved and
OL,9,Fit had reached an agreement with the
OL,10,Ftheatre "more than 10 years ago" that
OL,11,Fthe building was "not fit for purpose".
OL,13,FThe closure resulted in 70
OL,14,Fredundancies of staff, while plans for
OL,15,Fa new venue in the town centre's
OL,16,F'Cultural Quarter' were announced,
OL,17,Fscheduled to open in 2026.
