OL,3,CTheatre to re-open after help from
OL,4,Cfamous friends
OL,6,FA group of stars of stage and screen
OL,7,Fresponded by writing a letter to The
OL,8,FStage - an online site for UK theatre
OL,9,Fand performing arts - protesting that
OL,10,Fthe Coliseum should be saved.
OL,12,FFamous names who added their support
OL,13,Fto the letter included Julie
OL,14,FHesmondhalgh, Jim Broadbent, Dame
OL,15,FMaureen Lipman, Christopher Eccleston,
OL,16,FMaxine Peake, Sue Johnston, Barbara
OL,17,FKnox MBE and Sally Dynevor.
