OL,3,CTheatre to re-open after help from
OL,4,Cfamous friends
OL,6,FThe plan had been to close the theatre
OL,7,Fand build a new smaller arts centre
OL,8,Facross town, but Oldham Council has
OL,9,Fnow reversed the decision after
OL,10,Flistening to locals.
OL,12,FReacting to the news, Julie
OL,13,FHesmondhalgh says the theatre can be
OL,14,Fpart of Oldham's future and not just
OL,15,Fits past.
OL,17,F"I can't begin to tell you what an
OL,18,Fincredible moment this is," she said.
OL,19,F"It's a moment we didn't think could
OL,20,Fhappen."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
