OL,3,CTheatre to re-open after help from
OL,4,Cfamous friends
OL,6,FOldham Council leader Arooj Shah said:
OL,7,F"It's just the right thing to do, and
OL,8,Fsometimes to make decisions you have
OL,9,Fto lead with your finger on the pulse
OL,10,Fdo the right thing by people, and
OL,11,Fthat's what we did, we listened."
OL,13,FA new seven-strong board was appointed
OL,14,Ffor Oldham Coliseum Theatre Ltd and
OL,15,Fannounced ambitions to "preserve" and
OL,16,F"revitalise" the auditorium, extending
OL,17,Fit to include an expanded foyer,
OL,18,Fbackstage area, and cafe-bar space
OL,19,Fwhile creating studios and rehearsal
OL,20,Fspaces.
