OL,3,CTheatre to re-open after help from
OL,4,Cfamous friends
OL,6,FJane Barker is one of those who spear-
OL,7,Fheaded the campaign, creating the Save
OL,8,FOldham Coliseum group.
OL,10,F"I sat upstairs in the circle when the
OL,11,Flast curtain came down and it was
OL,12,Freally, really emotional, and you just
OL,13,Fthink I'm never going to see anything
OL,14,Fhere again," she said.
OL,16,F"But it's difficult to put into words
OL,17,Fbut I haven't taken the smile off my
OL,18,Fface since I heard the news."
