OL,3,CTheatre to re-open after help from
OL,4,Cfamous friends
OL,6,FAn Arts Council England spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "At Arts Council England, our
OL,8,Fpriority is to work with the people of
OL,9,FOldham to make sure that they have
OL,10,Faccess to the art and theatre that
OL,11,Fthey want - which is why we're
OL,12,Finvesting #1.845 million over three
OL,13,Fyears to support a creative and
OL,14,Fcultural programme in the borough,
OL,15,Fdelivered by partners including Oldham
OL,16,FColiseum Theatre Limited and Oldham
OL,17,FTheatre Workshop.
