OL,6,F"While the Coliseum building belongs
OL,7,Fto Oldham Council and isn't funded by
OL,8,Fthe Arts Council, we know what a well-
OL,9,Floved landmark it is, and recognise
OL,10,Fits link to the strong history of
OL,11,Ftheatre in the town, and the work the
OL,12,Fcampaign group has been doing to
OL,13,Fpreserve it."
